codex
Implemented REQ-026’s rollback substrate inside the execution framework.

The core API is in [rollback_checkpoints.py](/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/envctl/envctl-db-nu-plugin-migration-automation-package/execution-framework/scripts/rollback_checkpoints.py:105): it records hashed/idempotent checkpoint boundaries, validates blocked refs like secrets and key material, creates rollback handles, gates R3+ rollback plans through approvals, records lifecycle events, and enforces rollback status transitions.

